    viostor: Add missing virtio_device_shutdown call
    
    virtio_device_shutdown is a no-op because viostor doesn't use
    enough queues for the allocation code path. It should still be
    called though.

diff --git a/viostor/virtio_stor_hw_helper.c b/viostor/virtio_stor_hw_helper.c
